%h1.title
  Your coworking space is a mess?
  %br
  Some people never do anything in the office?

.homepage-hero
  .claim
    %span.m-headline_inverted SpongeHub helps you to keep your space
    %br
    %span.m-headline_inverted clean in a friendly and rewarding way.

  %ul.talking-points.unstyled
    %li Ideal for:  Coworking spaces, offices, shared flats.
    %li Reward people instead of being pushy.
    %li
      Clean when it fits
      %strong your
      schedule.
    %li Have fun as a team and enjoy your nice space!

  .sign-up
    - if current_user
      = link_to "Create a space!", [:new, :space], class: "sign-up--link"
    - else
      = link_to "Sign up!", root_path, class: "sign-up--link"

  .wischhand

%h2.m-headline.with-side-margin Participating spaces

%section.l-column-3
  -@spaces.each_with_index do |space, index|
    .l-column-3--column.m-box_polaroid{class: [("last" if (index+1)%3==0)]}
      = link_to image_tag(space.image_url(:homepage)), space, class: "m-box--image"
      = link_to space.name, space, class: "m-box--title"

%section.movie
  %iframe{:width => "420", :height => "315", :src => "http://www.youtube.com/embed/WuPShtmJKbI", :frameborder => "0"}